th: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0018.jpg 800w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0018-200x300.jpg 200w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0018-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0018-683x1024.jpg 683w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" /><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-301 size-full\" src=\"https://aconcept-uniform.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0019.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0019.jpg 800w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0019-200x300.jpg 200w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0019-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0019-683x1024.jpg 683w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-281 size-full\" src=\"https://aconcept-uniform.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/IMG_0007.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" />', 'ĐỒNG PHỤC NHÂN VIÊN KHÁCH SẠN', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dong-phuc-nhan-vien-khach-san', '', '', '2023-05-02 09:51:26', '2023-05-02 09:51:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/DOANWORDPRESS/wordpress/?post_type=khach_san&#038;p=166', 0, 'khach_san', '', 0),
