t-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ảnh-40-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ảnh-40-683x1024.jpg 683w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" /><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-394\" src=\"https://aconcept-uniform.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/%E1%BA%A3nh-41.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" srcset=\"https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ảnh-41.jpg 800w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ảnh-41-200x300.jpg 200w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ảnh-41-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://aconcept-uniform.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/ảnh-41-683x1024.jpg 683w\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" /></div>\r\n</div>', 'ĐỒNG PHỤC CÔNG SỞ CAO CẤP', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dong-phuc-cong-so-cao-cap-3', '', '', '2023-05-02 10:41:41', '2023-05-02 10:41:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost/DOANWORDPRESS/wordpress/?post_type=vanphong&#038;p=244', 0, 'vanphong', '', 0),
